01:36:12.281 --> 01:36:16.095
Sat-Chit-Anand. And third day I’ll be talking

01:36:16.296 --> 01:36:19.098
about Anand to you in Marathi language.

01:36:19.317 --> 01:36:25.413
I hope you will sit down and meditate on what I have said.

01:36:25.614 --> 01:36:28.959
