01:36:29.160 --> 01:36:32.445
But I want to protect you from what has happened

01:36:32.646 --> 01:36:35.542
to that culture and where it has gone,

01:36:35.754 --> 01:36:40.795
to bring you back to your own great culture,

01:36:40.996 --> 01:36:43.507
which came to us in thousands of years.

01:36:43.718 --> 01:36:46.986
Their culture is very, very, very new,

01:36:47.187 --> 01:36:49.133
it’s very new and one day they will also have

01:36:49.334 --> 01:36:51.267
the same culture as we have.

01:36:51.584 --> 01:36:54.037
But why not we short circuit it

01:36:54.311 --> 01:36:57.594
and adjust ourselves to this great culture,

01:36:57.795 --> 01:37:05.607
which is so much God oriented, not money oriented,

01:37:05.772 --> 01:37:09.642
ego oriented but God oriented?

01:37:09.843 --> 01:37:16.119
Let us all attain that state of yogi.

01:37:16.347 --> 01:37:18.791
I hope today it will happen to all of you

